4 (17) Supervisor. – A position that has other employees report directly to that
5 position.
6 (18) Temporary employee. – A State employee who is employed in a temporary
7 appointment for a limited term, including a State employee hired from the
8 OSHR Temporary Solutions Program, directly hired by an agency, hired by
