3 "§ 126A-56.3. Authorization to have applications considered for postings at other agencies;
4 job postings that apply to all agencies.
5 Each employing agency is granted flexibility, notwithstanding other provisions of this
6 Chapter, to do the following:
7 (1) Offer qualified applicants for employment the option to have their
