11 "Part 1. Paid Parental Leave and Bereavement Leave.
12 "§ 126A-70. Commission oversight of benefits that apply to all permanent positions.
13 (a) Subject to the approval of the Governor, the Commission may establish policies or
14 rules governing the following, including but not limited to:
15 (1) Paid parental leave.
16 (2) Bereavement leave.
17 (b) This Part applies to positions and employees otherwise exempt from this Chapter
