38 contributions under the Federal Insurance Contributions Act on account of the reduction in salary
39 may be used to pay some or all of the administrative expenses of the program. Should the Director
40 of OSHR decide to contract with a third party to administer the terms and conditions of a plan of
41 flexible compensation as provided by this section, it may select such a contractor only upon a
42 thorough and completely advertised competitive procurement process.
43 (d) As used in this section, the term "eligible officers and employees" means any officer
44 or employee authorized to participate in the Teachers' and State Employees' Retirement System,
45 the Consolidated Judicial Retirement System, the Legislative Retirement System, and the State
